Comment_glosser: Literally it is ‘one-zero’ for 10⋅ The further numerals are also built the same way, for example ‘23’ is ‘two-three’ or 56 is ‘five-six’⋅ These are probably made up numerals using just the verbal forms. The arithmetic opeartion is implicit in all the numbers.
